  }, {
    "tStartMs": 32160,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "wWinId": 1,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "No, there will be consequences.  Relationships deteriorate, and I'm constantly undervalued, but I have very little energy to talk back to anyone.  It's like the difference between a three-spotted wasp and a hornet.",
